Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: America's acid rain
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xkc1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Mar 1985
Reagan in top-level talks to halt US acid rain falling on Canada. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.